data.name: Leandro  'Lean' Álvarez
data.phrase: Sometimes the person that no one imagines capable of anything, ends up doing things that no one imagine.

data.name: Erica 'China' Soledad Curima
data.phrase: I try every day to change, even a little, to the world and, above all, resisting fiercely so that the world does not change me.

data.name: Román 'Maioneida' Mauro Diaz
data.phrase: We will were bond kicking and screaming until we learned to turn it down.
